Loggable - a simple log4j meta-library
Copyright (C) 2010  Daniele Di Bernardo
=======================================
 CHANGELOG
=======================================

v. 1.1.0
  - NEW: A class without the Loggable annotation will log in the default class-named logger
  - FIX: A tweak in the code will prevent a strange NullPointerException in the LoggerContainer class

v. 1.0.3
  - FIX: A bug in the LoggerContainer class caused an endless loop when asking for a void logger or the root logger

v. 1.0.2
  - FIX: A bug in the LoggerContainer class caused a NullPointerException under certain (rare) circumstances

v. 1.0.1
  - FIX: A bug in the LoggerContainer class caused a stack overflow when calling Log.get()

v. 1.0
  - First official release